<br>
No, I'm not saying Paladins should get this spell.  But something along those lines would be great.  Basically a spell which reduces damage taken by a certain percentage.<br>
<br>
That's what every super powerful thing in EQ is ... a percentage based effect (just like all the powerful stuff in Diablo II is percentage based).  Defensive is powerful not because it reduces all damage by 100, it is powerful because it reduces all damage ~50%.  Complete Heal is powerful because it heal 100% of hit points, not 1000 or 2000 or whatever (I know it actually heals 10k, but practically, it is a 100% heal).<br>
<br>
A self only spell which reduces all damage taken by say 30% with a decent duration would be nice.  A long recast time.  Basically, a discipline.<br>
<br>
Or a targettable spell, which reduces damage by say 20%, with a decent duration, with a very long recast time.  For example duration 3 minutes recast time 15 minutes (just like defensive).  Then multiple Paladins would be desired on raids, to continue casting this Sanctuary like spell after the first one ran out.<br>
<br>
